Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Scene three: Lights up on the headmasters office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.37,0:00:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The place is in shambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor Ginny holds the diary in one hand and rips through drawers and cabinets with the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Voldemort looks up at a portrait of Hogwart's former headmaster Albus Dumbledore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:23.40,Tom,,0,0,0,,AHHHH, Dumbledore! You old fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:28.57,Tom,,0,0,0,,I know that you hid the resurrection stone in here somewhere. And I'm gonna find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:31.60,Tom,,0,0,0,,Keep looking, slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.60,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Ginny, what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:35.48,Tom,,0,0,0,,Oh shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:39.28,Tom,,0,0,0,,Get - get rid of her! Get rid of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:47.88,Tom,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hahahaha, that's right, I forgot, she can't see me unless she touches the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:51.91,Tom,,0,0,0,,Just the same rules as 'death note'...\N[No reference necessary ;-)]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:55.22,Tom,,0,0,0,,They sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.62,Tom,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I just thought I'd say that out loud for your benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:02.62,Tom,,0,0,0,,Ore anyone's, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:06.62,Tom,,0,0,0,,The hell are you looking at me for? I said: Get rid of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:11.71,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Ginny, destroying the headmaster's office is definitely against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:15.22,Hermione,,0,0,0,,You know what, you've been acting like a real rule breaker, ever since you got your hands on that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:16.65,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Diary!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.71,0:01:16.94,Tom,,0,0,0,,Journal!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:25.00,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Wait a second... I remember. The deatheaters where after that thing for some reason. \NYou know what, Ginny? I think you'd better let me hold on to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:26.14,Ginny,,0,0,0,,Uhuhu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.02,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Gimme the diary, you spaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:32.34,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Accio, diary!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:35.40,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Tom Marvolo Riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:42.34,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Wait a second. If I take this letter and I put it there, and then... \N[mumbeling that's drawn out by the laughs from the audience]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:43.37,Hermione,,0,0,0,,It reads:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:46.17,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Am I Lord Vorldemort?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:49.08,Tom,,0,0,0,,No! I AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:50.71,Tom,,0,0,0,,Lord Voldemort!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:54.28,Hermione,,0,0,0,,No! No! Y-y-you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:55.45,Tom,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:58.02,Hermione,,0,0,0,,But... Harry killed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:01.62,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Dumbledore destroyed all the horcruxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:08.34,Tom,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dumbledore only thought he destroyed all of the horcruxes, but he missed one. One that was hidden until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:09.48,Hermione,,0,0,0,,The diary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.00,Tom,,0,0,0,,That's right, the journal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.11,Hermione,,0,0,0,,That means, that you're the heir of Slytherin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:18.37,Hermione,,0,0,0,,You're the one, who's been letting out the Chamber of Secrets' monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:21.34,Tom,,0,0,0,,Ooooh, oooooh, oooh - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:25.17,Hermione,,0,0,0,,So why are you petrifying everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:29.31,Tom,,0,0,0,,*laughs* You mean besides for the fun of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:32.85,Tom,,0,0,0,,Well, I hate to break it to you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.74,Tom,,0,0,0,,It's a red herring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:41.05,Tom,,0,0,0,,To keep you idiots distracted while I search for the real prize:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:43.05,Tom,,0,0,0,,The resurrection stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:48.31,Tom,,0,0,0,,And once I find it, I'll be back and there's nobody left who can stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:51.57,Tom,,0,0,0,,Now the bitch is back, and there's hell to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:03:01.20,Tom,,0,0,0,,You do realize, now that I've completely divulged my evil plan, you have to be... silenced?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.20,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna... are you gonna kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:04.85,Tom,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:07.97,Tom,,0,0,0,,I think, I'll just keep you on ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.97,Tom,,0,0,0,,Save you for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:12.22,Tom,,0,0,0,,Slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.97,Tom,,0,0,0,,Summon my giant snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.02,Tom,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:22.80,Tom,,0,0,0,,And Hermione,...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.05,Tom,,0,0,0,,I'd run if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:31.45,Hermione,,0,0,0,,To anyone who finds this note:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:37.77,Hermione,,0,0,0,,Destroy the diary! AHHHHH...
